Subject: We Appreciate Your Application and Participation

Body:
<html>
<body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#000000;font-size:14px;line-height:1.38;margin:0;padding:0;">
<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong style="font-weight:700">Hi [applicant_first_name],</strong></span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Thank you for taking the time to participate in the final interview for the <strong style="font-weight:700">[job_title]</strong> position. We truly appreciate the effort you invested in completing your application and sharing your experience, skills, and insights with us.</span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">We wanted to take a moment to sincerely thank you for your time and participation throughout the process.</span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">We encourage you to stay connected - follow us on our social media channels to stay updated on our latest opportunities:</span></span></p>

<ul style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.38;color:#000000;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:16px;padding-left:22px;">
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/OPGteam/" style="color:#1155cc;text-decoration:underline">Facebook</a></li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/_opgteam/" style="color:#1155cc;text-decoration:underline">Instagram</a></li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;">TikTok</li>
<li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/outsourced-pro-global/" style="color:#1155cc;text-decoration:underline">LinkedIn</a></li>
</ul>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">You're also welcome to refer others who may be a great fit.</span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">It was a pleasure learning more about you, and we sincerely value your interest in joining Outsourced Pro Global.</span></span></p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong style="font-weight:700">Recruiter contact:</strong> [recruiter_phone_line]</span></span></p>

[signature]
</body>
</html>
